Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon. There, that's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.46,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear someone is after your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help me! There's an assassin here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! The Master's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi-sama has been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I fear she could be an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man Magoroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might have hired another assassin besides us to do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired. Rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long must I do these kind of jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dissatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the shinobi, must do this to stay alive during this long period of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,soon the world will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood, the smell of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I've brought the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this enough for my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up against a great man this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, do you know anything about another female shinobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A female shinobi? Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, you'd expect them to be working as bodyguards or as hitmen for hire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will complete the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, her skills are quite adequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Karyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's that little one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you, you thief of a raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was supposed to be for the guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you off today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You little... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoto, hand me that raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuu is a giant flying squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, that doesn't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me, Saki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Magoroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get busy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still a child, so you don't need to hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done talking with Aoi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the reason I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fondle these more, soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, has something weird happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi spoke in a strange tone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu-sama, won't you join us for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you do is eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Karyuu-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is it true that someone tried to interfere with you last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, th-that's just what Saki-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back here. Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a bath, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.51,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,[The Bakufu was the military bureaucracy of the Tokugawa shogunate.]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems as if the Bakufu has really lowered its standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending a different woman each day to an outsider like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're trying to get me to face that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone killed me, the ranks of the Bakufu's enemies would decrease dramatically. {... wow}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fearsome man. {is fearsome the right word here? :V}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely came here to be of service, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe you should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I can't stop myself from making a little mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord, there's an assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the final moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood? Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood! Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were my foolish men?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.49,0:24:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.45,0:24:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? And you did that? You're brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.79,0:24:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that shinobi who flew in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.25,0:24:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so unskillful?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.01,0:25:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have great skills, and on top of that, your body is glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.27,0:25:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this. Will you work for me instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.57,0:25:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll top the other's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.86,0:25:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the kind of shinobi that will become increasingly useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.16,0:25:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the offer.
